<question type="multichoice">
  <name format="html">
    <text><![CDATA[ID-Fubini-02]]></text>
  </name>
  <questiontext format="html">
    <text><![CDATA[<p>Si \(R=[a,b]\times [c,d]\) es un rectángulo y \(f\) es continua, el teorema de Fubini afirma que: </p>]]></text>
  </questiontext>
  <defaultgrade>1.0</defaultgrade>
  <generalfeedback format="html"><text/></generalfeedback>
  <penalty>0.10</penalty>
  <hidden>0</hidden>
  <single>true</single>
  <shuffleanswers>1</shuffleanswers>
  <answernumbering>abc</answernumbering>
  <answer fraction="100" format="html">
    <text><![CDATA[<p>\(\displaystyle \iint _R f&#8239;dA = \int _a^b\!\!\int _c^d f(x,y)&#8239;dy&#8239;dx = \int _c^d\!\!\int _a^b f(x,y)&#8239;dx&#8239;dy\)</p>]]></text>
  </answer>
  <answer fraction="0" format="html">
    <text><![CDATA[<p>\(\displaystyle \iint _R f&#8239;dA = \int _a^b f(x,y)&#8239;dx\)</p>]]></text>
  </answer>
  <answer fraction="0" format="html">
    <text><![CDATA[<p>\(\displaystyle \iint _R f&#8239;dA = \int _a^b\!\!\int _c^d f(x,y)&#8239;dy&#8239;dx\) solo en ese orden.</p>]]></text>
  </answer>
  <answer fraction="0" format="html">
    <text><![CDATA[<p>\(\displaystyle \iint _R f&#8239;dA = \left (\int _a^b f&#8239;dx\right )\left (\int _c^d f&#8239;dy\right )\) siempre.</p>]]></text>
  </answer>
</question>
 
