<question type="multichoice">
  <name format="html">
    <text><![CDATA[IDP-Lin-01]]></text>
  </name>
  <questiontext format="html">
    <text><![CDATA[<p>La propiedad de linealidad de la integral doble establece que: </p>]]></text>
  </questiontext>
  <defaultgrade>1.0</defaultgrade>
  <generalfeedback format="html"><text/></generalfeedback>
  <penalty>0.10</penalty>
  <hidden>0</hidden>
  <single>true</single>
  <shuffleanswers>1</shuffleanswers>
  <answernumbering>abc</answernumbering>
  <answer fraction="100" format="html">
    <text><![CDATA[<p>\(\displaystyle \iint _R (af+bg)&#8239;dA = a\iint _R f&#8239;dA + b\iint _R g&#8239;dA\)</p>]]></text>
  </answer>
  <answer fraction="0" format="html">
    <text><![CDATA[<p>\(\displaystyle \iint _R (f\cdot g)&#8239;dA = \iint _R f&#8239;dA \cdot \iint _R g&#8239;dA\)</p>]]></text>
  </answer>
  <answer fraction="0" format="html">
    <text><![CDATA[<p>\(\displaystyle \iint _R (f+g)&#8239;dA = \iint _R f&#8239;dA \cdot \iint _R g&#8239;dA\)</p>]]></text>
  </answer>
  <answer fraction="0" format="html">
    <text><![CDATA[<p>\(\displaystyle \iint _R (af)&#8239;dA = \iint _R f&#8239;dA\)</p>]]></text>
  </answer>
</question>
<question type="multichoice">
  <name format="html">
    <text><![CDATA[IDP-Adit-01]]></text>
  </name>
  <questiontext format="html">
    <text><![CDATA[<p>Si \(R = R_1 \cup R_2\), donde \(R_1\) y \(R_2\) no se solapan (salvo en su frontera), entonces: </p>]]></text>
